{"tid":805154,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"最近先發現SpeedTest得100mbps. 求救.","createTime":"2018-09-03T14:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T15:24:36.000Z","uid":185607,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46c48adb121ffaa6de98a01e4662a11504ad81e2","tid":805154,"uid":185607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"小弟用緊HKBN1000M光纖入屋, 平時好少注意上網速度. 最近同個Friend吹奏左輪佢HKBN幾威啦, 跟住手痕手去Speedtest度run左下發現居然得95Mbps.我上返隻router個firmware睇返log, 發現100Mbps左都好長時間. 嚇到我個Friend blacklist左HKBN.<br />\n所以我即刻Check返曬我覺得我Check到既野.<br />\n<br />\n首先MB係有Gbe<br />\nrouter絕對係AC<br />\n線之前用緊HKBN俾既5e.我索性呢兩日轉晒做Cat6e<br />\n跟住發現上speedtest同直插電腦用返HKBN自己個speedtest, 居然都係得95Mbps.<br />\n我又換咪Notebook黎試亦都係95Mbps.<br />\nD機boot得既我都boot左, 連HKBN個webpage入邊既reset terminal我都reset埋.<br />\n結果都係一Q樣.<br />\n<br />\n請問我咩漏左？求救."},{"pid":"5dc2fab9329d505e81628d629ce4cb2f0f07e7d7","tid":805154,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:13:41.000Z","msg":"剛剛test完，發現得返264mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n睇返results七月嗰陣都仲有914mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32f144d4ae1fb81e8ec66df0874ad40914b8309","tid":805154,"uid":185607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc2fab9329d505e81628d629ce4cb2f0f07e7d7","tid":805154,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:13:41.000Z","msg":"剛剛test完，發現得返264mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n睇返results七月嗰陣都仲有914mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"有264咁多<i